{"id": 1556, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些时刻你觉得自己的计算能力是负的？", "description": "4个人吃饭花了240还要用手机计算器除一下人均，感觉自己从未学过数学。（题图来自：Tiago Galo）", "record_count": 16119, "comment_count": 53, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703071452053orROEFZimLDBP5t.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-08T17:00:04Z", "questions": [{"id": 2012, "title": "哪些时刻你觉得自己的计算能力是负的？", "content": "哪些时刻你觉得自己的计算能力是负的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 175766, "content": "网购的时候对“包邮”有执念，结果明明别家加上运费价格也更低", "image": "img/option/option/20170307150704iNJmXMkqKlyHzUdI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 176325, "content": "为了凑免邮的价格，买了一堆完全没用的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170308114448cBiV6Ua98RjdEIvz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175779, "content": "挑手机的时候觉得没必要用最新款，结果一两年后就过时了", "image": "img/option/option/2017030715182496RoDlVmqawcrEML.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175783, "content": "觉得内存最小的手机功能也没啥不一样，买了之后才觉得完全不够用", "image": "img/option/option/201703081156092s1LPOqrTbGnD4zM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175795, "content": "越是急着出门越是搞不清出租车和地铁哪个能更早到", "image": "img/option/option/20170307153630HK9JjgLcOv6fy3m0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175823, "content": "买机票只看了价格，没看税费，餐食、托运额度什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20170308115341vGACdbsHBhNuXS9e.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175836, "content": "一边下单新包，一边对自己说用一年平均每天才几块钱。", "image": "img/option/option/20170307164429saoN56KTpvhxMH70.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175775, "content": "海淘的时候看定价很便宜，结账加上税和邮费就傻眼了", "image": "img/option/option/20170307151459B5kRc9qg4yn0SP6H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}